snippet.textDisplay:
My 18yr old godson was murdered a little over 6 months ago. He was shot in the head during a mass shooting memorial day weekend in NJ. All I could think about was him while watching this video. The Crazy thing is right after she says "We forget the words We never forget the feeling" @:40 mark it shows her wearing a necklace that says Boogie on it & That's my godsons nickname! Omg when I saw that I got chills like never before! The pain u experience when your favorite soul to ever walk this earth is violently stolen from you is absolutely indescribable. Much love to Lauren & Puma for making this masterpiece cuz Its helped me with my grieving process. It actually had me smiling through the tears. And I'm gonna add those last few lines of that poem to the memorial tattoo im getting for my god baby.. Keep ur head up Lauren! You got this girl & he still got u from them heavens above!
RIP Unique Anderson aka Boogie
RIP Nipsey Hussle
#ForeverLoved #ForeverMissed #TheMarathonContinues
